&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;					<p class="headline_meta"><span><a href="http://www.beyondthecrater.com/siege-of-petersburg-resources/units/confederate-units/confederate-infantry/south-carolina-infantry/6th-south-carolina-infantry/#comments" rel="nofollow">0 comments</a></span></p>
					<p class="headline_meta">in <span><a href="http://www.beyondthecrater.com/category/siege-of-petersburg-resources/units/confederate-units/confederate-infantry/south-carolina-infantry/" title="View all posts in South Carolina Infantry" rel="category tag">South Carolina Infantry</a></span></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text entry-content">
<p><em><em>Editor&#8217;s Note: <strong>Do you have information on this regiment’s role at the Siege of Petersburg</strong>?  Please <strong><a href="../contact/">contact us</a></strong> using the Contact button in the menu at the top of the screen.  We are happy to exchange information with other researchers.</em></em></p>
